message: "If you use this code, the released adapters, or the dataset, please cite the thesis (see preferred-citation)."
title: "Community-Moderation-LLM: Evaluating Open-Source LLMs for Community-Specific Content Moderation on Reddit"
abstract: "Code, configuration, and aggregate results for a BSc Capstone study on whether open-weight LLMs (Qwen3-14B with per-subreddit and pooled LoRA adapters) can stand in for human moderators on individual subreddits, each with its own rules and norms."
